data.description: Welcome to the prestigious Jamestown Landing community, located in Southern Howard County close to the Montgomery County border. Minutes to JHU/APL, NSA/Ft Meade, FDA, I95, ICC and various commuter options to travel. Convenient to both Maple Lawn and Burtonsville for ample choices for shopping and restaurants. Howard County is known for its parks and this location is ideal for all activities especially boating/kayaking/fishing on the reservoir at Rocky Gorge up the street! Inside this well-appointed brick front colonial is over 6300 sq ft of space. Features added to the CRAFTMARK built home included vaulted ceilings, front and rear bump outs, dual zone HVAC systems and more. Entering in the home, the open foyer leads to the main level with 9’ ceilings and hardwood floors. The home has been freshly painted. Natural light is abundant through the many full-size windows and by an open floor plan. Family room with gas fireplace is located open to the gourmet kitchen. The kitchen offers cherry cabinets, granite counter tops, and stainless steel appliances with gas cooking. Formal living and dining rooms, 1st floor library/den and powder room. There are 2 staircases leading to the 2nd level. Upstairs all the bedrooms are generously appointed and feature walk in closets. Spacious owners suite with vaulted ceilings, a sitting area, a spa bathroom, and dual walk in closets. The second en suite bedroom has a full bathroom. Bedrooms 3 and 4 share access to the 3rd full bathroom. The full walk- out basement is unfinished and has a French door, abundance of windows for natural light.  Plenty of room to add additional living space and a full size bath (bath hook up is roughed in). This beautiful home in a desirable location is a win win! Call your agent for a private tour today!
